tile.title: Hacktoberfest Contribute
tile.about: I actively participated in the renowned Hacktoberfest event organized by GitHub, where I made valuable contributions to an open-source project. It was an incredible opportunity to collaborate with the global developer community and contribute to the advancement of open-source software.
